B.amN=new A.c("From Diagram 6, Black's K-7h won't do. G*7i will end the game.")
B.aeY=new A.c("Back in Diagram 5, there is one move you can play to get yourself out of danger, which is...?")
B.a3e=A.a(s(["G6g-6h"]),t.s)
B.aac=new A.P(null,B.a3e,B.r)
B.alX=new A.c("By placing two Golds side by side to guard your King, you can buy time. In the yagura-opening, you are supposed to place your Gold on 6g, but when you get into the endgame, the Gold had better be on 6h for the defense.")
