B.a82=new A.P("Moves from Diagram 2-2:",B.a2v,B.j)
B.akz=new A.c("B*7g is the move to play here. Black takes a Bishop in exchange for a Rook, which is not a material loss. After White's S-2b, there is a very good move on Black's part, which is...?")
