B.ajo=new A.c("Diagram 2-1 shows where White, in an attempt to cope with Black's bo-gin (climbing Silver), has just dropped a Bishop on 5d. If P2d, Px2d, Sx2d as Black intends to play, White can then drop a Pawn on 2g blocking the Rook's path.")
