B.ajV=new A.c("If the Dragon instead of the Horse was in White's camp as in Diagram 1-3, Black can play +R2i after P*2b. In this way Black can place the Dragon on a vital point in just one move. But in Diagram 1-2, Black has to play two moves, i.e.,+B1b and +Bx3d, before the Horse comes to a good square.")
