B.agm=new A.c("The game began with the Hineri-bisha opening which led to a wild middlegame, with both players vying to set their own Rooks free from their entangled positions (sabaku). Diagram 2-1 shows where White has just played N4g+, closing in on Black's camp. Since the King's guard is rather thin, White's S*5i or +N5h could be quite devastating.")
