B.adE=new A.c("There are many variations to build a Yagura, and you can be flexible. Just remember to move your generals diagonally.")
B.afW=new A.c("You still have to move your Bishop so that the King can safely sit in the Yagura castle. So you play, B7i, B6h, K7i, and K8h. (Diagram 3)")
