B.aoh=new A.be(19,B.bs,"Don't Put King and Rook Close Together","Gyoku-hi sekkin su bekarazu",B.SY)
B.agj=new A.c("You might have heard about how the Fujii system and the Crab Silver diverge from the basic formation. They can be very effective indeed when employed by a skillful hand. But I advise you to learn the basics first and then attempt the trickier lines.")
B.afX=new A.c("Diagram 1-1 (up to S5g) is from one of the most popular openings: static Rook vs ranging Rook.")
