B.aiZ=new A.c("So long as you see the castle as a space secured for your King, you should push the edge Pawn thereby making more room for the King to breathe. However, if the opponent has also built up the Yagura castle, the opponent's attacking pieces will therefore be at your King's head. You may invite a premature clash by advancing the edge Pawn. So, do be careful. This is what the proverb teaches.")
