B.adW=new A.c("Against your P*1b, White has to respond with Lx1b. Then you will be able to realize your scheme and play Lx1d. Now Black's 3 are balanced against White's 2, since White is unable to drop a Pawn on 1b to support 1c. The edge attack is promised to succeed.")
