B.aeJ=new A.c("Lastly I would like you to note that this tesuji is not only meant for the endgame. Diagram 4-1 is from the twisting Rook opening, where White has just dropped a dangling Pawn on 8f. In order to cope with the coming P8g+, Black has three means:")
